reviewText: Two video documenters see the same story in the community that has formed in "Bar 'El Chino'".  In the bar there is music and dance and camaraderie Argentine style.  The lives of the videographers are missing that same camaraderie.  They are attracted to it at the bar, but struggle with it and with love in their own lives.  The story line is predictable, except when it is not.  Argentine dialect of Spanish with English subtitles.
